---
description: Rails 8 conventions for the sample todo app
alwaysApply: true
---

- Prefer Turbo Streams over custom JavaScript for UI updates.
- Keep migrations reversible.
- Use strong parameters (`params.expect(...)`) in controllers.
- Use `bin/rails generate` instead of hand-writing Rails boilerplate.
- Keep schema changes scoped to this todo app; do not import models or migrations from other projects.